summary: This is a Municipal Credit Union direct deposit distribution request form, dated July 5, 2019, authorizing the distribution of payroll or government payments. It lists a total distribution amount of $91.00 to a loan account and is signed by Nakeida Atwell David.

persons.name: Nakeida Atwell David
persons.context: The individual who signed the direct deposit distribution request form, authorizing the Municipal Credit Union to distribute their payroll or government payment.

events.title: Direct Deposit Authorization
events.description: Nakeida Atwell David signed a form authorizing Municipal Credit Union to distribute their direct deposit, with a total distribution amount of $91.00 designated for a loan account.

keyFacts: The document is a direct deposit distribution request form from Municipal Credit Union.
The form is dated July 5, 2019, and authorizes a total distribution of $91.00 to a loan account.
The form is signed by Nakeida Atwell David, who authorizes the credit union to make adjustments for any incorrect deposits.
